{
  "id": "64c7b4376ede98001ba5ca42",
  "title": "長恨歌",
  "created": 1690809402,
  "updated": 1690809575,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "64c7b4376ede98001ba5ca42",
      "text": "長恨歌",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809402,
      "updated": 1690809402
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b43c5e90c0000013026c",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/長恨歌 長恨歌 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809402,
      "updated": 1690809414
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4485e90c0000013026e",
      "text": ">「長恨歌」（ちょうごんか）は、中国唐の詩人[白居易]によって作られた長編の漢詩である。[陳鴻]の[長恨歌伝]によれば、[白居易]、[陳鴻]、[王質夫]の三人が[仙遊寺]に集まり、唐代の[玄宗]皇帝と[楊貴妃]のエピソードを語り合い感嘆した際、王質夫が「夫れ希代の事は、出世の才の之を潤色するに遭ふに非ずんば、則ち時と消没し、世に聞こえず。楽天は詩に深く、情に多き者なり。試みに為に之を歌はば、如何と。」（「世にも奇妙な出来事は、一代の傑出した才人の手で潤色されるのでなければ、時と共に消滅してしまって、世の中に伝わらなくなってしまう。楽天、君は詩に造詣が深く、情に豊かな人だ。試みにこの出来事で歌を作って見てはどうか」という意）と言われたことをきっかけに、「長恨歌」を作ったと書かれている。『[源氏物語]』をはじめ平安時代の日本文学にも多大な影響を与えた。806年（元和元年）、白居易が35歳、[盩厔県尉]であった時の作。[七言古詩]（[歌行]とも言う）（120句）。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809414,
      "updated": 1690809458
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b43c5e90c0000013026d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809402,
      "updated": 1690809402
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4825e90c0000013026f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809473,
      "updated": 1690809473
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4825e90c00000130270",
      "text": "> 漢皇重色思傾国　御宇多年求不得",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809473,
      "updated": 1690809485
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130272",
      "text": "> 楊家有女初長成　養在深閨人未識　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130274",
      "text": "> 天生麗質難自棄　一朝選在君王側　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130276",
      "text": "> 迴眸一笑百媚生　六宮粉黛無顔色　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130278",
      "text": "> 春寒賜浴華清池　温泉水滑洗凝脂　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013027a",
      "text": "> 侍児扶起嬌無力　始是新承恩沢時　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013027c",
      "text": "> 雲鬢花顔金歩揺　　　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013027e",
      "text": "> 芙蓉帳暖度春宵　　　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130280",
      "text": "> 春宵苦短日高起　従此君王不早朝　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130282",
      "text": "> 承歓侍宴無閑暇　春従春遊夜専夜　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130284",
      "text": "> 後宮佳麗三千人　三千寵愛在一身　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130286",
      "text": "> 金屋粧成嬌侍夜　玉楼宴罷酔和春　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130288",
      "text": "> 姉妹弟兄皆列土　可憐光彩生門戸　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013028a",
      "text": "> 遂令天下父母心　不重生男重生女　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013028c",
      "text": "> 驪宮高処入青雲　仙楽風飄処処聞　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013028e",
      "text": "> 緩歌慢舞凝糸竹　尽日君王看不足　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130290",
      "text": "> 漁陽鞞鼓動地来　驚破霓裳羽衣曲　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130292",
      "text": "> 九重城闕煙塵生　千乗万騎西南行　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130294",
      "text": "> 翠華揺揺行復止　西出都門百余里　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130296",
      "text": "> 六軍不発無奈何　宛転蛾眉馬前死　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809510
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130298",
      "text": "> 花鈿委地無人収　　　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013029a",
      "text": "> 翠翹金雀玉搔頭　　　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013029c",
      "text": "> 君王掩面救不得　迴看血涙相和流　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c0000013029e",
      "text": "> 黄埃散漫風蕭索　雲桟縈紆登剣閣　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302a0",
      "text": "> 峨眉山下少人行　旌旗無光日色薄　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302a2",
      "text": "> 蜀江水碧蜀山青　聖主朝朝暮暮情　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302a4",
      "text": "> 行宮見月傷心色　夜雨聞鈴腸断声　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302a6",
      "text": "> 天旋日転迴竜馭　到此躊躇不能去　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302a8",
      "text": "> 馬嵬坡下泥土中　不見玉顔空死処　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302aa",
      "text": "> 君臣相顧尽霑衣　東望都門信馬帰　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302ac",
      "text": "> 帰来池苑皆依旧　太液芙蓉未央柳　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302ae",
      "text": "> 芙蓉如面柳如眉　対此如何不涙垂　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302b0",
      "text": "> 春風桃李花開夜　秋雨梧桐葉落時　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302b2",
      "text": "> 西宮南苑多秋草　宮葉満階紅不掃　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302b4",
      "text": "> 梨園弟子白髪新　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302b6",
      "text": "> 椒房阿監青娥老　　　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302b8",
      "text": "> 夕殿蛍飛思悄然　孤灯挑尽未成眠　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302ba",
      "text": "> 遅遅鐘鼓初長夜　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302bc",
      "text": "> 耿耿星河欲曙天　　　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302be",
      "text": "> 鴛鴦瓦冷霜華重　翡翠衾寒誰与共　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302c0",
      "text": "> 悠悠生死別経年　魂魄不曾来入夢　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302c2",
      "text": "> 臨邛道士鴻都客　能以精誠致魂魄　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302c4",
      "text": "> 為感君王展転思　遂教方士殷勤覓　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302c6",
      "text": "> 排空馭気奔如電　昇天入地求之遍　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302c8",
      "text": "> 上窮碧落下黄泉　両処茫茫皆不見　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302ca",
      "text": "> 忽聞海上有仙山　山在虚無縹緲間　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302cc",
      "text": "> 楼閣玲瓏五雲起　其中綽約多仙子　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302ce",
      "text": "> 中有一人字太真　雪膚花貌参差是　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302d0",
      "text": "> 金闕西廂叩玉扃　　　　　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302d2",
      "text": "> 転教小玉報双成",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809556
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302d4",
      "text": "> 聞道漢家天子使　九華帳裏夢魂驚　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302d6",
      "text": "> 攬衣推枕起徘徊　珠箔銀屏邐迤開　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302d8",
      "text": "> 雲鬢半偏新睡覚　花冠不整下堂来　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302da",
      "text": "> 風吹仙袂飄颻挙　猶似霓裳羽衣舞　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302dc",
      "text": "> 玉容寂寞涙闌干　梨花一枝春帯雨　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302de",
      "text": "> 含情凝睇謝君王　一別音容両渺茫　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302e0",
      "text": "> 昭陽殿裏恩愛絶　蓬萊宮中日月長　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302e2",
      "text": "> 迴頭下望人寰処　不見長安見塵霧　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302e4",
      "text": "> 唯将旧物表深情　鈿合金釵寄将去　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302e6",
      "text": "> 釵留一股合一扇　釵擘黄金合分鈿　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302e8",
      "text": "> 但令心似金鈿堅　天上人間会相見　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302ea",
      "text": "> 臨別殷勤重寄詞　詞中有誓両心知　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302ec",
      "text": "> 七月七日長生殿　夜半無人私語時　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302ee",
      "text": "> 在天願作比翼鳥　在地願為連理枝　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c000001302f0",
      "text": "> 天長地久有時尽　此恨綿綿無絶期　　　　",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809474,
      "updated": 1690809474
    },
    {
      "id": "64c7b4835e90c00000130271",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1690809473,
      "updated": 1690809473
    }
  ]
}